				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\begin{aligned} \varDelta \approx \frac{N_H m_H^2}{N_Lm_L^2} \frac{4}{3+m_H/m_L}, \end{aligned}$$\end{document}where capital letters denote total stellar mass and lower-case letters individual masses of stars. The quantity Δ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
