Although observations suggest a large spread amongst the values of the relaxation time at the influence radius of MBHs with similar masses (see, e.g., Fig. 4 of Merritt et al. 2006), most galactic nuclei hosting MBHs less massive than a few 106M⊙\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
